race.comment: CINDY CABANG (3) is a promising type who notched her 5th career success when too good (16.91) at Healesville last time. Has a good record here including two wins. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. TRAJECTORY (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (22.62) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form here sound including two wins. Expected to give a good account. WEST TWO AFFAIR (7) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Has finished in the placings two on end now, the latest when second (19.69) at Healesville. Can feature again. WANDANA LAD (1) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.
